I"a<p>Sign In</p>

<p>Step-1: When you click on Risersoft ESS shortcut on your mobile screen, it shows splash screen then Authenticate page will appear.</p>

<p>Step-2: Enter your registered email id. Click on Next.
Then password field will appear. Enter your password. Password has been sent to your registered email. In case of Windows users or Imported users, password will be same as Windows password. Click on Sign In.</p>

<p>Step-3: Enter OTP which has been sent to your registered mobile number. If two factor authentication is false, there is no need for OTP.
After entering OTP, click on Sign In. Select account page will appear. Select your account.  If there is only one account, this page will not appear. It automatically connects to your account. Click on Submit.
After selecting account, dashboard with Employee name and employee code will appear.</p>
